    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resultare</strong>是一款受Peggle物理机制与Balatro奇妙组合启发的弹珠台类Roguelike游戏。在这场充满抉择、精准与混乱的对决中，你能找到完美协同效应突破配额吗？精心规划每次射击，解锁强力代币，构建独特组合，追逐更高分数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>一次尝试远远不够。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/98a0ac1f2dc4d5504a2b9329ea036315.poster.avif?t=1772052786\" width=1072 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/98a0ac1f2dc4d5504a2b9329ea036315.webm?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/98a0ac1f2dc4d5504a2b9329ea036315.mp4?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Resultare</strong>中，每次射击都是机遇。瞄准目标，见证令牌效果的滚雪球效应，同时努力达成分数目标。超过100种道具让每次挑战都独一无二，探索全新强力协同组合，重塑你的游戏风格！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/6f1b54a0d829cf4a5541066126196865.poster.avif?t=1772052786\" width=350 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/6f1b54a0d829cf4a5541066126196865.webm?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/6f1b54a0d829cf4a5541066126196865.mp4?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色亮点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120+ 符文自由组合，打造无穷战术体系</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ 道具卡提供战术优势与玩法变数</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ 精工打造的关卡待你征服</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ 头目竭力阻挠你的前进</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 种解锁玩法模式彻底改变游戏体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 种难度设置满足挑战爱好者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来更新还将持续追加内容！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/b8dd9e75faf5ec385f54f9e497ad2ef5.poster.avif?t=1772052786\" width=350 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/b8dd9e75faf5ec385f54f9e497ad2ef5.webm?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/b8dd9e75faf5ec385f54f9e497ad2ef5.mp4?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩过程中解锁海量道具、难度与模式。在Resultare中你永远有目标可追——若这还不够，你还能抚摸猫咪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/a646b97c4c64ff346f79f13225b90433.poster.avif?t=1772052786\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/a646b97c4c64ff346f79f13225b90433.webm?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062650/extras/a646b97c4c64ff346f79f13225b90433.mp4?t=1772052786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
